<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12044g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12044g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12044g"> 44(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Night / prayer / icebath / sleep</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Saint Patrick]</font> divided the night into three parts. During the first he recited a hundred Psalms &hellip; he plunged into a vessel of icy cold water &hellip; The third part of the night was given to repose <small> Very Rev. Dean Kinane, <a name="TKSP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#TKSP"><cite title="source">St. Patrick: his life, his heroic virtues, his labours, and the fruits of his labours</cite></a>, (ed. unknown) 207</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
